ונעשה החלפת משתנים 
\begin_inset Formula $w=a_{1}x+b_{1}y\qquad z=a_{2}x+b_{2}y$
\end_inset

 ואז
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x=A_{1}w+B_{1}z\qquad y=A_{2}w+B_{2}z
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
